text: Morgongiori (Mragaxòri) is a town and comune (municipality) in the Province of Oristano in Sardinia, Italy. As of 2016, 720 people lived there. Its area is 45.2 km². It is 351 meters above sea level. == References == == Other websites == Category:Communes of the Province of Oristano
title: Morgongiori
